        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "For the most part, these cars were sheep in wolves' clothing. It's not GM's fault though, really – the one-two punch of a fuel crisis and new federal emissions standards really knocked the wind out of a lot of performance cars. The Camaro Z28 was no exception.",
